<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.2.7">
<l>kāmaṉṟaṉak kumuraiyallēṉ kaṭalvaṇṇaṉār</l>
<l>māmaṇavā ḷareṉakkuttā  ṉumakaṉcollil</l>
<l>yāmaṅkaḷtō ṟerivīcumeṉ ṉiḷaṅkoṅkaikaḷ</l>
<l>māmaṇivaṇṇar tiṟattavāy vaḷarkiṉṟavē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I have no complaints against Kāma. If [you] ask [why], the sea-hued one</l>
<l>Is [my] dark beloved; [so Kāma] is my son, [too.]</l>
<l>My young breasts, where he hurls flames all of the time,</l>
<l>Rise only because of the dark gem-hued one.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
